I can't put my finger on it.

514
00:30:39,129 --> 00:30:42,609
- 他不会说的
- 对…他不会说的
- He won't say.
- No... he won't say.

515
00:30:43,110 --> 00:30:45,659
- 荷叶，是吗？
- 荷叶，棒极了
- Lotus, right?
- Lotus, bravo.

516
00:30:46,674 --> 00:30:48,894
我喜欢口味上的不同
I like some conflict
in the flavors.

517
00:30:49,645 --> 00:30:50,601
