Excuse me,
but I know how Alexandre works.

543
00:32:02,909 --> 00:32:06,127
- 但是我就是亚历山大！
- 那又如何？有什么关系吗？
- But I'm Alexandre!
- So? How does that matter?

544
00:32:06,710 --> 00:32:08,768
我从一开始就跟随着亚历山大
I've followed Alexandre
since day one.

545
00:32:09,269 --> 00:32:10,555
你想听真相吗？
You want the truth?

546
00:32:11,119 --> 00:32:13,212
