她想给你看点婴儿用品
<i>She has baby stuff
to show you.</i>

611
00:35:43,901 --> 00:35:45,915
是吗？我会打她电话的
Oh yeah?
I'll call her back.

612
00:35:51,102 --> 00:35:52,662
