<i>stuck behind
some trucks.</i>

641
00:37:07,769 --> 00:37:09,066
等等，走啊！
Hold on. Move!

642
00:37:09,568 --> 00:37:11,994
我也要去工作！让我过去！
I have to work too!
Let me through!

643
